title: Asset Listing: Add $IDLE on ETH v1
body:
Asset Listing: Add $IDLE on ETH v1

Intro: This is a vote to list $IDLE on ETH v1 with a collateral factor and collateral cap.

Proposal: https://forum.cream.finance/t/proposal-add-idle-as-collateral-asset-on-cream/1753

Rationale: List $IDLE on ETH v1 market with collateral factor of 25% and collateral cap of $250k. Idle is a decentralized yield aggregator.

For:
List $IDLE on ETH v1 market with Collateral Factor: 25% and Collateral Cap: $250k.

Against:
Do nothing.
author: 0xd662fA474C0A1346a26374bb4581D1F6D3Fb2d94
